talkin' about her.

20:06.250 --> 20:08.417
-Who?
-His mom.

20:09.458 --> 20:11.166
It's what helped me.

20:14.917 --> 20:16.959
(thunder rumbling)

20:19.458 --> 20:21.375
Ruby.

20:21.458 --> 20:23.125
Ruby:
One second.

20:24.208 --> 20:25.792
Ruby.

20:37.750 --> 20:39.375
Have we made it?

20:40.458 --> 20:41.834
Yeah.

20:42.625 --> 20:44.667
The train's coming
in 20 minutes.

20:44.750 --> 20:46.875
